I love this bike because it’s reasonably priced and gives me the convenience of cycling from home instead of having to drive to a gym and do it. This bike has come in handy not only am I using it but my mom has created her own profile and is cycling too so we can both keep track of our goals.

settings.pages_swiper_title: Get this bike!!!! You won't regret it.
settings.pages_swiper_Info: Honestly I was a little hesitant to purchase this bike coming from Echelon products and never hearing of the brand before. Online customer experience via chat was extremely helpful. Shipping was really fast, assembly was straightforward. I LOVE the instructors, the class variety, challenges - I've been on my bike daily and am upset I waited so long to find it. Oh, and it's PINK!!!! Yay =)

I can’t compare my bike with any other products in the market, but I can tell you that I did do my research before buying and loved all its awesome features, especially the automatic resistance! I enjoy working out with the coaches and love their music selections. I also participate in the toning and stretching out. Overall well worth it!

settings.pages_swiper_title: Old girls can do it too!
settings.pages_swiper_Info: I'm a beginner rider and at first the idea of riding was daunting, but this beginner 15 minute class I took this morning made it fun and easy! The instructor was very upbeat and positive and encouraging! I was even able to ride after the class for the additional beats challenge for another 5 to 7 minutes. I'm feeling good I'm now ready to face the day!

It's small enough to fit in a bedroom, apartment, etc taking up minimal real estate. It has an area to hold weights. It is exciting, fun, tons of classes, trails for leisure riding and is ever growing challenges and classes for prizes. Who doesn't love an Amazon gift card to incentive a workout. The lights are so fun and the music is great. My whole family loves the bike and the price was affordable compared to other bikes.

settings.pages_swiper_title: The best addition to my home!
settings.pages_swiper_Info: I love all of the classes FreeBeat offers!!! Between the new scenic routes and excellent instructors for cycling class or weight lighting and stretching. I am hooked and can’t get enough! They also offer prizes every month for riding!! Also my bike is pink. It’s so beautiful!! I’ve had my bike almost a full year now and I highly recommend this brand!!

settings.bury_freebeat_title: Why Invest in Indoor Exercise Bikes From freebeat™?
settings.bury_freebeat_info1: Our indoor exercise bikes are a sleek, attractive, and easy addition to any home — even ones short on space. That’s thanks to our unique compact design. These bikes are bonafide beauties and come in a lovely range of colors matching your home aesthetic.
settings.bury_freebeat_info2: Our freebeat™ bikes might be pretty and compact, but don’t be fooled by appearances. They also contain an entire home gym with instructors and friends with whom you can compete. With the simple tap of your 180-degree rotating HD touch screen, you can choose from thousands of interactive workout classes and exercise experiences taught by rockstar instructors across the country. Your freebeat™ workout will be tailored to your unique needs with real-time performance tracking and technology that intuitively matches your resistance level with your abilities and pace.

settings.bury_freebeat_title: What Features Make freebeat™ Exercise Bikes Unique?
settings.bury_freebeat_info1: At freebeat™, we have revolutionized the way people work out. Our exercise bikes are the world’s only home fitness equipment that offers fully gamified workouts. This feature puts you right into the action of your workout as if you are the main character of a video game. Your classes will be interactive and engaging, with artist-generated visuals, a killer soundtrack, and plenty of opportunities to befriend and compete against athletes around the country. You can even invite your real friends to play against you.
settings.bury_freebeat_info2: Our indoor exercise bikes are also unique in their aesthetic. Traditionally, workout machines can be pretty clunky and ugly. They are all substance, no style. At freebeat™, we wanted to provide both. Our bikes offer a serious workout, but they also look cute in your home.

settings.bury_freebeat_title: What Types of Classes Can I Take With My freebeat™ Bike?
settings.bury_freebeat_info1: The sky's the limit! Your freebeat™ exercise bike comes loaded with thousands of engaging, gamified classes and workout experiences for athletes of every level. Choose from special cycling themes like music or holidays, or try a gamified high-intensity interval training (HIIT) session. Our classes can be customized to match your pace and ideal resistance intuitively, so you’ll always be smashing the right workout for your needs.
